      "difficulty_level": "easy",
      "score_points": 1.0
    },
    {
      "point_id": 3,
      "question_type": "true_false",
      "question_content": "如果函数f(x)在x=a处的左极限等于右极限，则f(x)在x=a处一定连续。",
      "question_options": [
        {"label": "A", "content": "正确", "is_correct": false},
        {"label": "B", "content": "错误", "is_correct": true}
      ],
      "correct_answer": "B",
      "explanation": "详细解析：即使函数在某点的左极限和右极限相等，也不能保证该点处的函数值等于极限值，因此不能确定函数在此点连续。",
      "difficulty_level": "medium",
      "score_points": 1.0
    },
    {
      "point_id": 4,
      "question_type": "fill_blank",
      "question_content": "函数f(x)=x²在x=2处的导数是：_____。",
      "question_options": null,
      "correct_answer": "4",
      "explanation": "填空解析：根据导数定义，f'(x) = lim(h→0) [(f(x+h)-f(x))/h]。代入f(x)=x²，计算得f'(2) = 2*2 = 4。",
      "difficulty_level": "easy",
      "score_points": 1.0
    },
